      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REFEREES (2) in great order in his first prep and unlucky not to have a few more wins on the CV. Surged late from the wide draw with a narrow third over 1175m at this track. Returned good figures on that occasion and should relish the extra ground. Hard to stop. CASINO COLLECTION (9) no match for REFEREES two-back, then got off the mark with a fast finishing victory over 1300m at Taree. Key runner who can go through the grades. XTREME (3) gone to a new level for the new yard and comes here deep into the prep. Struggled to run the 1600m out with a plugging second at Taree. Winning rider hops back on and expected to be competitive back to the 1420m. HIGHWIRE GIRL (6) surprised first-up over the unsuitable trip with a respectable sixth over 1175m at this track. Blinkers come off and clearly returned in good order. Expected to take a hand in the finish.",
